  <div class="row">
	  <div class="col-lg-11 col-lg-offset-1">
		  <h4 class="text-left">Ehdrigohr (<a href="https://council-of-fools.com/blog/ehdrigohr-rpg/" target="_blank">council-of-fools.com/blog/ehdrigohr-rpg</a>, Allen Turner)</h4>
